snippet.title: Kingdom Tales 2 for iPhone and iPad
snippet.description:
Princess Dahla was the most beautiful and cleverest in the land. But she was secretly in love with a young blacksmith named Finn. Join the quest to help Finn expand her father’s kingdom. Can he prove his worth – and win the right to marry Dahla?  

Play on iPad: https://itunes.apple.com/ua/app/kingdom-tales-2-hd/id960639511?mt=8
Play on iPhone: https://itunes.apple.com/ua/app/kingdom-tales-2/id960636244?mt=8
